    },
    {
      "locale": "zhCN",
      "text": "“我不会解释的。我就是对的，就这么简单。”",
      "modification_date": "2026-04-14T10:07:10.6174102Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-04-14T10:07:10.6174114Z",
      "original_text": "\"I would not. I'm right, and that's all there is to it.\"",
